# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Expunge None
Create Slave

# More sections follow
#
# !!!! Note that empty lines delimit sections !!!!

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User linn.official@gmail.com
# Use 'pass show' to securely fetch your Gmail App Password
PassCmd "pass show app-passwords/official_gmail_k9 | head -n 1"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPs
# Omit if you want to use the system certificate store.
#CertificateFile ~/.server-certificate.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path /home/linn/.local/share/linn/mail/official-gmail/
Inbox /home/linn/.local/share/linn/mail/official-gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *

